Package: passport
Type: Package
Title: Travel smoothly between country name and code formats
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Edward", "Visel", email = "edward.visel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: passport smooths the process of working with country names and 
    codes via powerful parsing, standardization, and conversion utilities 
    arranged in a simple, consistent API. Country name formats include multiple 
    sources including the Unicode CLDR common-sense standardizations in 
    hundreds of languages.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Inports:
    stats, 
    utils
Suggests:
    jsonlite, 
    DT, 
    ggplot2, 
    ggmap,
    googleway,
    testthat,
    covr
